OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FShake firm Huel's ads      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbanned for being misleading
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Adverts that suggested Huel meal       
OL,6, replacement shakes could save people   
OL,7, money on their food bills have been    
OL,8, banned for being misleading.           
OL,10,FAs the cost of living crisis hit, one  
OL,11,FFacebook ad claimed that "Huel helps   
OL,12,Fkeep money in your pockets".           
OL,14,FBut Huel did not show its products were
OL,15,Fcheaper than traditional food, the     
OL,16,FAdvertising Standards Authority said.  
OL,18,FThe firm, which has pulled the ads,    
OL,19,Fsaid it took its advertising           
OL,20,Fresponsibilities seriously.            
